00:54:42,121 --> 00:54:46,762
Scott: And you should try to, you know, see all the crazy, crazy cool things people have been able to mount.

988
00:54:46,802 --> 00:54:54,240
Scott: Like you can mount your friggin scanner and, you know, when you scan something, a JPEG appears in that folder and then you read it out.

