01:03:42,801 --> 01:03:43,250
Rym: SMB CFS.

1137
01:03:44,100 --> 01:03:46,177
Scott: No, at the end and whatever it is.

1138
01:03:46,601 --> 01:03:47,619
Rym: Oh, NTFS.

1139
01:03:47,860 --> 01:03:49,236
Scott: Yeah, NTFS derp derp.

1140
01:03:49,740 --> 01:03:51,900
Rym: Well, CFS common Internet file system.

1141
01:03:52,623 --> 01:03:53,517
Scott: NTFS is a file system.

